videos.headline: Miss. State keeps clock moving after sack with time expiring
videos.description: Nick Fitzgerald gets sacked with time expiring while Mississippi State and Florida decide not to call a time out.

videos.headline: Florida scores game's 1st TD on trick play
videos.description: In the third quarter, Florida executes a double-pass to score the game's first touchdown.
